INSERT INTO `experimental_description` VALUES ('8', '命令自整', '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24pt; font-family: PingFang&nbsp;SC, Microsoft&nbsp;YaHei, sans-serif;\"><strong>Vue命令自整</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p>1.创建项目<span style=\"white-space: pre;\"> </span>vue init webpack&nbsp; &ldquo;项目名称&rdquo;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>2.安装依赖<span style=\"white-space: pre;\"> </span>npm install</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>3.启动项目<span style=\"white-space: pre;\"> </span>npm run dev</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>（&darr;安装好模块需重新npm install&darr;）</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>4.安装axios模块 <span style=\"white-space: pre;\"> </span>npm install --save axios vue-axios&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>5.安装router模块<span style=\"white-space: pre;\"> </span>npm install vue-router -save-dev</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>6.安装element-ui<span style=\"white-space: pre;\"> </span>npm i element-ui -S</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>7.安装sass加载器<span style=\"white-space: pre;\"> </span>npm install sass-loader node-sass -save-dev</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>使用淘宝镜像安装<span style=\"white-space: pre;\"> </span>npm install --registry=http://registry.npm.taobao.org</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>npm run dev 错误提示：{ parser: \"babylon\" } is deprecated; we now treat it as { parser: \"babel\" }.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>解决方法：npm install prettier@~1.12.0 --save-dev</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>tinymce编辑器安装：npm install tinymce -S&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;npm install @tinymce/tinymce-vue -S</p>', '2020-07-10 12:56:26');
